About Talaria

Named after the winged sandals of Hermes, Talaria represents speed, elevation, and the relentless pursuit of athletic excellence.

Our Mission

Talaria exists to empower the next generation of athletes with performance gear that doesn't break the bank. We believe that every athlete, from high school basketball players to weekend gym warriors, deserves access to equipment that enhances their performance and supports their athletic journey.

Who We Serve

Our target market is active teens and young adults who play sports like basketball and football and regularly train at the gym. They want high-quality, durable, performance-enhancing athletic gear that is comfortable, stylish, and affordableâ€”helping them train harder and compete at a higher level.

Our Approach

We focus on three core principles: performance, durability, and accessibility. Every product in our catalog is designed with the serious athlete in mind, featuring advanced materials, ergonomic designs, and practical innovations that make a real difference in training and competition. Unlike premium brands that price out young athletes, Talaria offers competitive pricing without sacrificing quality.

The Competition

While we respect the innovation of industry leaders, Talaria carves its own path by combining performance features with accessible pricing. We compete with:

Nike
Adidas
Under Armour

Looking Forward

As Talaria grows, our commitment remains unchanged: to provide athletes with the gear they need to reach new heights, without the premium price tag. Like the wings that inspire our name, we're here to help you soar.

Shipping Information

Delivery Options

At Talaria, we understand you need your gear fast. We offer multiple shipping options to get your performance equipment to you as quickly as possible.

Standard Shipping

Cost: FREE on orders over $75
Delivery Time: 5-7 business days
Available to all addresses in the continental United States.

Express Shipping

Cost: $12.99
Delivery Time: 2-3 business days
Perfect when you need your gear for an upcoming game or event.

Overnight Shipping

Cost: $24.99
Delivery Time: 1 business day
Order by 2 PM EST for next-day delivery (Monday-Friday).

International Shipping

We currently ship to Canada and select international locations. Shipping costs and delivery times vary by destination. International orders may be subject to customs fees and import duties.

Order Tracking

Once your order ships, you'll receive a confirmation email with tracking information. Track your package in real-time to know exactly when your Talaria gear will arrive.

Returns & Exchanges

Our Guarantee

We stand behind the quality of our products. If you're not completely satisfied with your Talaria purchase, we offer a straightforward return and exchange policy.

30-Day Return Window

You have 30 days from the date of delivery to return any item for a full refund or exchange. Products must be unworn, unwashed, and in original condition with all tags attached.

How to Return an Item

1. Contact our customer service team at returns@talaria.com
2. Include your order number and reason for return
3. We'll provide a prepaid return shipping label
4. Pack items securely in original packaging
5. Drop off at any authorized shipping location

Refund Processing

Once we receive your return, we'll inspect the items and process your refund within 5-7 business days. The refund will be credited to your original payment method.

Exchanges

Need a different size or color? Exchanges are processed as quickly as possible. We'll ship your replacement item as soon as we receive your return.

Damaged or Defective Items

If you receive a damaged or defective product, contact us immediately at support@talaria.com. We'll arrange a free return and send a replacement at no charge.

Size Guide

Finding Your Perfect Fit

Proper fit is essential for peak performance. Use our comprehensive size guide to find the right size for all Talaria products.

Apparel Sizing

Compression Shirts & Base Layers

Small: Chest 34-36", Waist 28-30"
Medium: Chest 38-40", Waist 32-34"
Large: Chest 42-44", Waist 36-38"
X-Large: Chest 46-48", Waist 40-42"
XX-Large: Chest 50-52", Waist 44-46"

Training Leggings

Small: Waist 28-30", Inseam 28"
Medium: Waist 32-34", Inseam 30"
Large: Waist 36-38", Inseam 32"
X-Large: Waist 40-42", Inseam 32"

Equipment Sizing

Gloves: Measure around your palm at its widest point (excluding thumb)
Belts: Measure around your natural waist where you'd wear the belt
Shoulder Pads: Based on chest measurement and player position
Footballs & Basketballs: Available in official regulation sizes and youth sizes

Still Not Sure?

Contact our customer service team at support@talaria.com for personalized sizing assistance. We're here to help you find the perfect fit.

Frequently Asked Questions

Ordering & Payment

What payment methods do you accept?

We accept all major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover), PayPal, and Apple Pay for your convenience.

Is it safe to order online?

Absolutely. Our website uses industry-standard SSL encryption to protect your personal and payment information. Your data is secure with us.

Shipping & Delivery

How long does shipping take?

Standard shipping takes 5-7 business days. We also offer Express (2-3 days) and Overnight options for faster delivery.

Do you ship internationally?

Yes, we ship to Canada and select international locations. Shipping costs and delivery times vary by destination.

Returns & Exchanges

What is your return policy?

We offer a 30-day return window for unworn items in original condition. Returns are free and easy with our prepaid shipping labels.

How do I exchange an item?

Contact our customer service team to initiate an exchange. We'll send your new item as soon as we receive the returned product.

Product Information

Are Talaria products suitable for competitive sports?

Yes! Our products are designed for serious athletes and meet all requirements for competitive play in basketball, football, and gym training.

How do I care for my Talaria gear?

Most apparel items are machine washable in cold water. Hang dry or tumble dry low. Check individual product tags for specific care instructions.
